{"tid":1308709,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[革命電影系列]","createTime":"2019-07-12T03:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T05:16:05.000Z","uid":186808,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"66921d178c4e307a468609e8d0d4d2ebfb8b3b11","tid":1308709,"uid":186808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:14:38.000Z","msg":"最近嘅事，令到我覺得香港人唔再係我心目中咁政治冷感 開始暖化  係令到我由心覺得有希望<br />\n<br />\n哩個post主要係推介一啲有關革命，抗爭主題嘅電影。其中內容情節未必同現時香港情況好有關。但係當中抗爭嘅精神，行動中嘅心情，大局變化 等，希望大家可以參考下。<br />\n<br />\n經過連日行動，有啲資訊疲勞，大家可以睇戲抽離1,2個鐘，重拾初衷。<br />\n<br />\n我會嘗試先post一啲Netflix 上睇到嘅戲/新啲嘅戲先<br />\n無時間睇晒成套的話，可以睇youtube 一啲scene。"},{"pid":"03ff0796d4d2c9491a91b99cf0547ee555e23f33","tid":1308709,"uid":186808,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:15:37.000Z","msg":"[Netflix] V for Vendetta《V煞》2005 (132min) IMDB 8.2/10<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.adventuresinpoortaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/990E6D94-B41C-47BB-A960-BD3D61B2C488-e1550115650765.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.adventuresinpoortaste.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F990E6D94-B41C-47BB-A960-BD3D61B2C488-e1550115650765.jpeg&h=e3b8b47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哩套戲最為人熟悉，應該係Iconic 嘅V面具<br />\n喺2011年 佔領華爾街 運動當中，唔小人選擇戴住V mask<br />\n而V mask 就係代表 主角V 心中想要傳達畀民眾嘅嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://thefifthwave.files.wordpress.com/2014/07/v-at-ows.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthefifthwave.files.wordpress.com%2F2014%2F07%2Fv-at-ows.png&h=c3e19de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n改編自DC comics, 哩套戲 係一個 個人對政權 復仇嘅故事。戲名雖然係講 復仇 但係最終係好有感染力<br />\n<br />\n故事背景: 未來嘅英國，人民因為戰爭，用自由 換取 安穩，直到所有人都對暴政 不公義 監控已經習慣，對 自由 已經無希望。<br />\n<br />\n主角V 係一個神秘優雅嘅人，而佢只有一個目標，就係要報仇。佢選擇用暴力，weapon of choice：刀。以暴逆暴， 係有原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n============================================<br />\n<br />\n[Spoiler alert]<br />\n無時間可以睇youtube 一啲我覺得幾好睇嘅片段<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wKn1R6fekk4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwKn1R6fekk4&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0K%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=13f24c6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wKn1R6fekk4</a><br />\nV 自我介紹<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KKvvOFIHs4k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKKvvOFIHs4k&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0K%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=49e2158f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KKvvOFIHs4k</a><br />\nV嘅公開演講<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 可以嘅話睇英文字幕<br />\n亮點：Natalie Portman + Agent Smith<br />\nHigh Chancellor 好似陶傑"},{"pid":"0a70ddb23b6c23fafc466b3c5a08a05a63e0a606","tid":1308709,"uid":260654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:17:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1f073be23300839df9d491047a5b99d6d8cb1d9","tid":1308709,"uid":269148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"Beneath this mask there is more than flesh, Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr. Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof."},{"pid":"6bd3cd5912162bdc092e23dd1b1cfdee4435fae6","tid":1308709,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:42:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6889cb005e8a1b37bcd474ad4667582b774b33cd","tid":1308709,"uid":186808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:26:52.000Z","msg":"[Netflix] Winter on Fire: Ukraine's Fight for Freedom 《凜冬烈火：烏克蘭為自由而戰》 (2015) (102min) IMDB 8.4/10<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/22/Winter_on_Fire.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F22%2FWinter_on_Fire.png&h=73552bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哩套唔係一套fiction，係一套紀錄片，係真實發生嘅事。<br />\n當中紀錄烏克蘭於2013-2014年冬天爆發嘅公民運動。<br />\n<br />\n事件源於當時總統承諾簽署協定，將加入歐盟，列為歐洲國家。但又反口，激起民眾不滿，上街抗議。<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭人民一直渴望擁抱西方價值觀及自由，同時恐懼國家再次受俄羅斯控制。<br />\n<br />\n事件過程大家可以自己去睇，喺呢度唔多講。<br />\n<br />\n推介哩套野，係因為好多情況同香港抗爭有直得參考之處。例如點樣面對防暴部隊，集結市民。<br />\n<br />\n要留意烏克蘭嘅局勢係俾香港嚴苛好多，天氣，防暴級別等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.abc.net.au/news/image/5145870-3x2-700x467.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2Fimage%2F5145870-3x2-700x467.jpg&h=812f289d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但烏克蘭好清晰佢地面對咩問題，係政府背棄人民期望同價值觀。而要有哩個focus，係要依靠每人自己獨立嘅思考，如果有足夠數量，思想類近嘅平民，無任何事物可以停止阻止到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.112.international/original/2016/01/27/208125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.112.international%2Foriginal%2F2016%2F01%2F27%2F208125.jpg&h=54e1e955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人一樣，要睇到上街終極目標係咩 大家嘅不滿源自咩 邊個要負責 你要佢點樣負責。</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">（共產黨，離開香港）</span></span><br />\n但個人認為打壓力道越大，市民反彈越大。而現在香港係冷處理，反動。<br />\n希望大家睇完會反思。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.abc.net.au/news/image/5214112-3x2-700x467.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2Fimage%2F5214112-3x2-700x467.jpg&h=550abee8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.abc.net.au/news/image/5214110-3x2-700x467.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2Fimage%2F5214110-3x2-700x467.jpg&h=9fc4c864&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.abc.net.au/news/image/5143196-3x2-700x467.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2Fimage%2F5143196-3x2-700x467.jpg&h=95628942&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d06a2ab62c499bbda7f25de886c40d1c24bff554","tid":1308709,"uid":186808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6889cb005e8a1b37bcd474ad4667582b774b33cd","tid":1308709,"uid":186808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:26:52.000Z","msg":"[Netflix] Winter on Fire: Ukraine's Fight for Freedom 《凜冬烈火：烏克蘭為自由而戰》 (2015) (102min) IMDB 8.4/10<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/22/Winter_on_Fire.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%